spec_data.Name: perl-Module-CPANTS-Analyse
spec_data.Description:
CPANTS is an acronym for CPAN Testing Service. The goals of the CPANTS project
are to provide some sort of quality measure (called "Kwalitee") and lots of
metadata for all distributions on CPAN.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:25:37 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Generate Kwalitee ratings for a distribution
